Package com.teampc.model.test

Model classes used to describe the layouts of different kinds of tests, including Take Home, Practice, and In Class Tests.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GradedTest
    GradedTest representins a test after it has been graded.
    InClassTest
    InClassTest represents a test to be taken during a class session
    PracticeTest
    PracticeTest is a test that won't count towards an official grade
    TakeHomeTest
    A Test that can be taken home and completed on the student's own time
    Test
    Test represents all test objects handled by the application.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TestDifficulty
    TestDifficult is an enumeration representing the difficulty of a test.
